memes.description: Crime has skyrocketed in my neighborhood.
Happy 40th anniversary to the movie Gremlins! Remember when we found out Luck Skyrocketâ€™s dad was a Cylon? So scary!

I live to vacation another day!: First day lounging on a beach in many, many years. Was very cautious and avoided getting any sunburn anywhere, which as a pasty white Brit used to sitting in the semi-darkness staring at a computer screen all day is very good going.

I'm all shook up: We all just sat down to our meeting, and we're doing introductions went I felt the building begin to sway a bit, and then it really started to feel like it was bouncing up and down. I was like, "What the shi....!" As I wanted to stay formal at the job club, I didn't finish that sentence. The shaking was powerful enough that the computer chair I was sitting was trying to compensate for the shaking with its internal hydraulic piston. I even made a playlist https://open.spotify.com/playlist/6oPxFwtsgCgiw9HQlFcdXy?si=r9mH7GhNTQigXrsq88J4OA&pi=u-zXIrOTYNR-mo
